snippet.title: Path of Exile 2: Dawn of the Hunt Teaser
snippet.description:
In two weeks tune in to twitch.tv/pathofexile to get all the information about our next content update for Path of Exile 2! 

During the livestream you'll learn all about the 0.2.0 content update for Path of Exile 2. After the livestream, Jonathan and Mark will answer your burning questions live in a Q&A session with ZiggyD, which we will follow up with the full 0.2.0 patch notes.

You'll be able to play the 0.2.0 content update on PC and Consoles on April 4th (PDT). We are very excited to show you what we've been working on!

ru.title: Path of Exile 2: Тизер контентного обновления 0.2.0
ru.description:
Через две недели подключайтесь к twitch.tv/pathofexile, чтобы узнать всё о следующем контентном обновлении для Path of Exile 2!

Во время прямой трансляции вы узнаете все подробности о контентном обновлении 0.2.0 для Path of Exile 2. После стрима Джонатан и Марк ответят на самые горячие вопросы в прямом эфире во время Q&A-сессии с ZiggyD. Затем мы опубликуем полный список изменений версии 0.2.0.

Дополнение 0.2.0 будет доступно для игры на ПК и консолях 4 апреля (PDT). Мы с нетерпением ждём момента, когда сможем показать вам, над чем работали!

en-GB.title: Path of Exile 2: Content Update 0.2.0 Teaser
en-GB.description:
In two weeks tune in to twitch.tv/pathofexile to get all the information about our next content update for Path of Exile 2! 

During the livestream you'll learn all about the 0.2.0 content update for Path of Exile 2. After the livestream, Jonathan and Mark will answer your burning questions live in a Q&A session with ZiggyD, which we will follow up with the full 0.2.0 patch notes.

You'll be able to play the 0.2.0 content update on PC and Consoles on April 4th (PDT). We are very excited to show you what we've been working on!

ko.title: 패스 오브 엑자일 2: 0.2.0 콘텐츠 업데이트 티저
ko.description:
2주 후, twitch.tv/pathofexile에서 패스 오브 엑자일 2의 다음 콘텐츠 업데이트에 대한 모든 정보를 공개합니다!

이번 라이브스트림에서는 패스 오브 엑자일 2의 0.2.0 콘텐츠 업데이트에 대한 상세 내용을 확인할 수 있습니다. 방송이 끝난 후에는 Jonathan과 Mark가 ZiggyD와 함께 실시간 Q&A 세션을 진행하며, 이후 0.2.0 패치노트 전체 내용도 공개할 예정입니다.

0.2.0 콘텐츠 업데이트는 4월 5일 (한국 시각) PC 및 콘솔에서 플레이할 수 있습니다. 

새로운 콘텐츠를 여러분께 선보일 생각에 무척 기대됩니다!

th.title: Path of Exile 2: ทีเซอร์แพทช์อัพเดทเนื้อหา 0.2.0
th.description:
ติดตามชมข้อมูลแพทช์ใหม่สำหรับ Path of Exile 2 กันได้ที่ twitch.tv/pathofexile ในสองสัปดาห์ข้างหน้านี้!

ในการถ่ายทอดสดนี้ คุณจะได้รู้ข้อมูลต่างๆ เกี่ยวกับแพทช์อัพเดทเนื้อหา 0.2.0 สำหรับ Path of Exile 2 และเมื่อการถ่ายทอดสดจบลง โจนาธานกับมาร์คจะมาร่วมกับ ZiggyD เพื่อตอบคำถามคาใจของคุณกันสดๆ ในช่วงตอบคำถามค่ะ และเราจะปิดท้ายด้วยการอัพรายละเอียดแพทช์ตัวเต็มให้อ่านกัน

คุณจะได้เล่นแพทช์อัพเดทเนื้อหา 0.2.0 ในระบบ PC และคอนโซลในวันที่ 5 เมษายนนี้ (เวลาไทย) เราตั้งตารอนำเสนอผลงานของเราอยู่นะคะ!

de.title: Path of Exile 2: Teaser zum Content-Update 0.2.0
de.description:
Seid in zwei Wochen live auf twitch.tv/pathofexile dabei, um alles Wichtige über unser nächstes Content-Update für Path of Exile 2 zu erfahren!

Während des Livestreams erfahrt ihr alles zum Content-Update 0.2.0 für Path of Exile 2. Nach dem Livestream werden Jonathan und Mark in einer Live-Fragerunde mit ZiggyD eure brennenden Fragen beantworten, wonach wir die vollständigen Patch-Notes für 0.2.0 veröffentlichen werden.

Am 4. April erscheint das Content-Update 0.2.0 für PC und Konsolen. Wir freuen uns darauf, euch zu zeigen, woran wir gearbeitet haben!

zh-Hant.title: 《流亡黯道2》：內容更新 0.2.0 預告片
zh-Hant.description:
兩個禮拜後，準時收看 twitch.tv/pathofexile，獲得《流亡黯道2》下一個內容更新的所有資訊！

 在實況期間，玩家將能得知《流亡黯道2》0.2.0 內容更新的所有情報。 實況結束後，Jonathan 與 Mark 會在直播中的問與答環節，與 ZiggyD 一起回答玩家迫切想知道的問題，並在隨後附上完整的 0.2.0 更新檔說明。

 從 4 月 5 日開始，玩家就可以在 PC 和主機上玩到 0.2.0 內容更新。 我們等不及想讓各位看看我們的成果了！

ja.title: Path of Exile 2:コンテンツアップデートティーザー
ja.description:
2週間後、twitch.tv/pathofexile にて、Path of Exile 2の次回コンテンツアップデートに関する最新情報をお届けします！

ライブ配信では、Path of Exile 2の0.2.0 コンテンツアップデートに関する詳細を紹介します。ライブ配信の後、JonathanとMarkがZiggyDと共に皆さんの疑問にお答えします。そして、配信の後には0.2.0のパッチノート全文も公開予定です。

0.2.0 コンテンツアップデートは4月5日 (日本時間)にPCおよびコンソールでプレイ可能になります。私たちが取り組んできたアップデートをお見せするのが待ちきれません！

fr.title: Path of Exile 2 : teaser de la mise à jour de contenu 0.2.0
fr.description:
Dans deux semaines, rendez-vous sur twitch.tv/pathofexile afin de tout savoir à propos de notre nouvelle mise à jour de contenu pour Path of Exile 2 ! 

Pendant le stream d'annonce en direct, vous découvrirez tout ce qu'il y a à savoir à propos de la mise à jour 0.2.0 de Path of Exile 2. Après le stream d'annonce, Jonathan et Mark répondront à vos questions les plus pressantes dans le cadre d'une session de Q&R en compagnie de ZiggyD, suivie des patch notes complètes de la 0.2.0.

Vous pourrez jouer à la version 0.2.0 à partir du 4 avril (CEST) sur PC et consoles. Nous sommes impatients de vous dévoiler tout ce sur quoi nous avons travaillé !

pt-BR.title: Path of Exile 2: Teaser da Atualização de Conteúdo 0.2.0
pt-BR.description:
Em duas semanas, fique ligado em twitch.tv/pathofexile para ver todas as informações sobre a nossa próxima atualização e conteúdo para o Path of Exile2!

Durante a transmissão, você terá mais informações sobre a atualização de conteúdo 0.2.0 para o Path of Exile. Após a transmissão, Jonathan e Mark responderão suas perguntas mais frequentes em uma sessão de Q&A com ZiggyD, com as notas do patch saindo logo em seguida.

Você poderá jogar a atualização de conteúdo 0.2.0 gratuitamente no PC e nos Consoles no dia 4 de Abril. Estamos muito empolgados para mostrar no que temos trabalhado!

en.title: Path of Exile 2: Dawn of the Hunt Teaser

es.title: Adelanto de la actualización 0.2.0 de Path of Exile 2
es.description:
¡En dos semanas, ven a twitch.tv/pathofexile para obtener toda la información sobre nuestra próxima actualización de contenido para Path of Exile 2! 

Durante la transmisión en vivo, descubrirás todo sobre la actualización de contenido 0.2.0 de Path of Exile 2. Después de la transmisión, Jonathan y Mark responderán todas tus preguntas en una sesión de Q&A con ZiggyD, al final de la cual publicaremos las notas completas del parche 0.2.0.

Podrás jugar la actualización de contenido 0.2.0 en PC y consolas el 4 de abril PDT. ¡Estamos muy ansiosos por mostrarte todo en lo que hemos estado trabajando!

snippet.title: SHOULD YOU TOW WITH A CYBERTRUCK?! - (catastrophic failure test)
snippet.description:
The Tesla Cybertruck is built with a cast aluminum frame. Get up to 40% off your RIDGE wallet here: https://www.ridge.com/JERRYRIG (discount code: JerryRig) Huge thanks to RIDGE for sponsoring my science projects. This helps the cyber truck be manufactured extremely quickly. However - cast aluminum is not good for towing as we see in this Cybertruck durability test video. The hitch breaks around 10,000 pounds. (4500kg) Which is far too close to the 11,000 pound towing capacity. Yikes. 

While the Gigacasting method is *terrible* for the Cybertruck it is actually an amazing manufacturing process for Tesla's other vehicles which i highly recommend: https://ts.la/zack10701

If you want an electric truck that can still tow 11,000lbs and not snap in half - might i recommend a Rivian: https://rivian.com/configurations/list?reprCode=ZACK1594426

snippet.title: Sir Jim Ratcliffe: Amorim, Ten Hag, Finances & The Glazers | The Overlap With Gary Neville
snippet.description:
Gary Neville is joined by Sir Jim Ratcliffe on The Overlap, brought to you by Sky Bet. They discuss Manchester United’s season so far, new manager Ruben Amorim, the club’s finances, and what’s next for United.

Ratcliffe reflects on his first year at United, including the controversial decision to replace Erik ten Hag with Ruben Amorim, despite an FA Cup triumph. He also tackles the club’s financial struggles, including a bloated wage bill, and the steps being taken to bring United back to the top.

The conversation also lifts the lid on Dan Ashworth’s departure, what really happened behind the scenes, and how it impacted United’s plans heading into a crucial second half of the Premier League season.

Looking ahead, Gary and Sir Jim discuss the future of Old Trafford, the club’s long-term vision, and whether United fans can find reasons for optimism after a below-par campaign.

Don’t miss this one—hit like, share your thoughts in the comments, and subscribe to stay updated with every episode!

snippet.title: SIDEMEN CHARITY MATCH 2025 [OFFICIAL STREAM]
snippet.description:
Sidemen Charity Match 2025

Donate here: https://www.sidemenfc.com 

On the 8th of March Sidemen FC and YouTube Allstars are coming together to play the 2025 Charity Match at Wembley Stadium.

Use the hashtag #SDMNCharityMatch to talk about the game!

OFFICIAL STREAM starts at 2:10pm GMT

Kick off time is at 3pm GMT

The Sidemen Charity Match 2025 is in aid of the following charities and funds raised will be split as follows:

Bright Side 43%
BBC Children in Need 50%
M7 Education 7%

We will also donate all of the profit we make through the match and related activities to the following charities:

Bright Side 86%
M7 Education 14%

Any donations you make are greatly appreciated and going to great causes! We hope you enjoy the match.

For full details and terms and conditions please visit https://sidemenfc.com.

Viewers of this livestream are strictly prohibited from re-streaming or rebroadcasting this content on any platform. Any unauthorised re-streaming will result in the immediate removal of the infringing livestream and a copyright strike issued to the violator.

snippet.title: Finding A Player Who Doesn't Exist
snippet.description:
I received a message on discord from someone asking if I could help them find a friend they hadn't spoken with in a while. The task seemed innocent enough at first, but ended up being one of the most mysterious and darkest rabbit holes I've ever investigated. What happened to Alex? This is finding a minecraft player who doesn't exist.

Channel: @xXCraftykinggXx 

➤➤ Twitter: https://twitter.com/WifiesWasTaken
➤➤ Discord: https://discord.gg/zAWUuWb


➤➤Links: I dont think any? but maybe I'm forgetting 


This is a series called Minecraft VVSauce where I explore random features of Minecraft. Not Secret Minecraft things or Minecraft lore (like Game Theory) or Escape Rooms, but a scary arg based series. The footage in this video isn't of a real person, an ARG is a story that's known to be fictional but we all pretend it's real and try to solve the mystery that the owner of this channel created. Such is the life of an ARG hunter. Very scary very creepy. BOO!

snippet.title: Hiking To The CIA’s “Top Secret” Plane Crash in Death Valley
snippet.description:
Check out the best electrolyte mix out there at https://drinklmnt.com/Brent for a FREE 8-count sample pack! I take LMNT everywhere with me, especially on these long hikes.

In this video, I finally attempt a hike to the legendary crashed CIA plane in the middle of Death Valley. 

This plane was part of a top secret program in the 1950s as part of the United State's Cold War efforts. The program was a joint program between the Air Force and the CIA. Unfortunately, on one cold night in January of 1952, one of these planes crashed on a training mission over Death Valley. 

Due to the remote and difficult nature of getting to the airplane, it was left there. Now, 73 years later, I hiked in to see what it was all about!

I hope you enjoy!

You can follow my journey on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/brentwunderwood/

Cerro Gordo T-Shirts and more: https://store.cerrogordomines.com/ 

Mailing Address: PO Box 490, Lone Pine, CA 93545

pt-BR.title: Caminhada até o acidente de avião “ultrassecreto” da CIA no Vale da Morte
pt-BR.description:
Confira a melhor mistura de eletrólitos disponível em https://drinklmnt.com/Brent para um pacote de amostra GRÁTIS de 8 unidades! Levo LMNT para todos os lugares comigo, especialmente nessas longas caminhadas.

Neste vídeo, finalmente tento fazer uma caminhada até o lendário avião da CIA que caiu no meio do Vale da Morte. 

Este avião fazia parte de um programa ultrassecreto na década de 1950 como parte dos esforços dos Estados Unidos na Guerra Fria. O programa era um programa conjunto entre a Força Aérea e a CIA. Infelizmente, em uma noite fria de janeiro de 1952, um desses aviões caiu em uma missão de treinamento sobre o Vale da Morte. 

Devido à natureza remota e difícil de chegar ao avião, ele foi deixado lá. Agora, 73 anos depois, fiz uma caminhada para ver do que se tratava!

Espero que gostem!

Você pode acompanhar minha jornada no Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/brentwunderwood/

इस वीडियो में, मैं आखिरकार डेथ वैली के बीच में दुर्घटनाग्रस्त हुए CIA के प्रसिद्ध विमान तक पहुँचने का प्रयास करता हूँ।

यह विमान 1950 के दशक में यूनाइटेड स्टेट्स के शीत युद्ध प्रयासों के तहत एक शीर्ष गुप्त कार्यक्रम का हिस्सा था। यह कार्यक्रम वायु सेना और CIA के बीच एक संयुक्त कार्यक्रम था। दुर्भाग्य से, जनवरी 1952 की एक ठंडी रात में, इनमें से एक विमान डेथ वैली के ऊपर एक प्रशिक्षण मिशन पर दुर्घटनाग्रस्त हो गया।

हवाई जहाज तक पहुँचने की दुर्गम और कठिन प्रकृति के कारण, इसे वहीं छोड़ दिया गया। अब, 73 साल बाद, मैं यह देखने के लिए वहाँ गया कि यह सब क्या था!

it.title: Escursione al luogo dell'incidente aereo "top secret" della CIA nella Death Valley
it.description:
Dai un'occhiata al miglior mix di elettroliti in circolazione su https://drinklmnt.com/Brent per un campione GRATUITO da 8 pezzi! Porto LMNT ovunque con me, soprattutto durante queste lunghe escursioni.

In questo video, provo finalmente a fare un'escursione sul leggendario aereo della CIA precipitato nel mezzo della Death Valley.

Questo aereo faceva parte di un programma top secret negli anni '50 come parte degli sforzi degli Stati Uniti durante la Guerra Fredda. Il programma era un programma congiunto tra l'aeronautica militare e la CIA. Sfortunatamente, in una fredda notte di gennaio del 1952, uno di questi aerei si schiantò durante una missione di addestramento sulla Death Valley.

A causa della natura remota e difficile per raggiungere l'aereo, è stato lasciato lì. Ora, 73 anni dopo, ho fatto un'escursione per vedere di cosa si trattava!

Spero che ti piaccia!

fr-FR.title: Randonnée vers le crash de l'avion « top secret » de la CIA dans la Vallée de la Mort
fr-FR.description:

Dans cette vidéo, je tente enfin une randonnée jusqu'au légendaire avion de la CIA écrasé au milieu de la Vallée de la Mort.

Cet avion faisait partie d'un programme top secret dans les années 1950 dans le cadre des efforts de la guerre froide des États-Unis. Malheureusement, par une nuit froide de janvier 1952, l'un de ces avions s'est écrasé lors d'une mission d'entraînement au-dessus de la Vallée de la Mort.

ja.title: デスバレーの CIA の「極秘」飛行機墜落現場へのハイキング
ja.description:
https://drinklmnt.com/Brent で最高の電解質ミックスをチェックして、8 個入りの無料サンプル パックを手に入れましょう。私はどこへ行くにも LMNT を持っていきます。特に長いハイキングのときは。

このビデオでは、デス バレーの真ん中で墜落した伝説の CIA 飛行機へのハイキングに挑戦します。

この飛行機は、1950 年代に米国の冷戦対策の一環として極秘で実施されたプログラムの一部でした。このプログラムは空軍と CIA の共同プログラムでした。残念ながら、1952 年 1 月のある寒い夜、この飛行機の 1 機がデス バレー上空の訓練ミッション中に墜落しました。

飛行機にたどり着くのが遠くて困難だったため、飛行機はそのまま残されました。73 年経った今、私はハイキングして、一体何だったのか確かめてきました。

お楽しみください。

de-DE.title: Wanderung zum „streng geheimen“ Flugzeugabsturz der CIA im Death Valley
de-DE.description:
Schauen Sie sich die beste Elektrolytmischung an, die es gibt, unter https://drinklmnt.com/Brent und erhalten Sie ein KOSTENLOSES 8er-Probepaket! Ich nehme LMNT überall mit hin, besonders auf diese langen Wanderungen.

In diesem Video versuche ich endlich eine Wanderung zu dem legendären abgestürzten CIA-Flugzeug mitten im Death Valley.

Dieses Flugzeug war in den 1950er Jahren Teil eines streng geheimen Programms im Rahmen der Bemühungen der Vereinigten Staaten im Kalten Krieg. Das Programm war ein gemeinsames Programm der Air Force und der CIA. Leider stürzte in einer kalten Nacht im Januar 1952 eines dieser Flugzeuge bei einem Trainingseinsatz über dem Death Valley ab.

Da das Flugzeug so abgelegen und schwer zu erreichen war, wurde es dort zurückgelassen. Jetzt, 73 Jahre später, bin ich dorthin gewandert, um zu sehen, was es damit auf sich hatte!

Ich hoffe, es gefällt Ihnen!

Sie können meine Reise auf Instagram verfolgen: https://www.instagram.com/brentwunderwood/

Cerro Gordo T-Shirts und mehr: https://store.cerrogordomines.com/ 

Postanschrift: PO Box 490, Lone Pine, CA 93545

DANKE!

id.title: Mendaki ke Lokasi Kecelakaan Pesawat “Rahasia” CIA di Death Valley
id.description:
Lihatlah campuran elektrolit terbaik di https://drinklmnt.com/Brent untuk mendapatkan paket sampel 8 hitungan GRATIS! Saya membawa LMNT ke mana-mana, terutama pada pendakian yang panjang ini.

Dalam video ini, saya akhirnya mencoba mendaki ke pesawat CIA legendaris yang jatuh di tengah Death Valley. 

Pesawat ini merupakan bagian dari program rahasia pada tahun 1950-an sebagai bagian dari upaya Perang Dingin Amerika Serikat. Program ini merupakan program gabungan antara Angkatan Udara dan CIA. Sayangnya, pada suatu malam yang dingin di bulan Januari 1952, salah satu pesawat ini jatuh saat menjalankan misi pelatihan di Death Valley. 

Karena jaraknya yang jauh dan sulit untuk mencapai pesawat tersebut, pesawat itu ditinggalkan di sana. Sekarang, 73 tahun kemudian, saya mendaki untuk melihat seperti apa pesawat itu!

Semoga Anda menikmatinya!

Anda dapat mengikuti perjalanan saya di Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/brentwunderwood/

Kaos Cerro Gordo dan lainnya: https://store.cerrogordomines.com/ 

Alamat Surat: PO Box 490, Lone Pine, CA 93545

TERIMA KASIH!

snippet.title: Harvey Specter Is Back | Suits LA | NBC
snippet.description:
Harvey Specter has officially landed on the West Coast. 

All-new Suits LA - watch NBC on Peacock.

#NBC #SuitsLA

» Subscribe for More: http://bit.ly/NBCSub

NBC ON SOCIAL:
YouTube: http://www.youtube.com/nbc
Twitter: http://Twitter.com/NBC
Facebook: http://Facebook.com/NBC
Instagram: http://instagram.com/nbc

Find NBC trailers, full episode highlights, previews, promos, clips, and digital exclusives here. 

ABOUT SUITS LA:
Ted Black, a former federal prosecutor from New York, has reinvented himself to represent the most powerful clients in Los Angeles. His firm is at a crisis point, and in order to survive, he must embrace a role he held in contempt his entire career. Ted is surrounded by a stellar group of characters who test their loyalties to both Ted and each other while they can’t help but mix their personal and professional lives. All of this is going on while we slowly unravel the events that years ago led Ted to leave behind everything and everyone he loved.

The series stars Stephen Amell, Lex Scott Davis, Josh McDermitt and Bryan Greenberg. Aaron Korsh is writer and executive producer. David Bartis, Doug Liman, Gene Klein, Anton Cropper, Genevieve Sparling, Rick Muirragui and Jon Cowan also executive produce. “Suits LA” is produced by UCP, a division of Universal Studio Group.

ABOUT SUITS LA:
Ted Black, a former federal prosecutor from New York, has reinvented himself to represent the most powerful clients in Los Angeles. His firm is at a crisis point, and in order to survive, he must embrace a role he held in contempt his entire career. Ted is surrounded by a stellar group of characters who test their loyalties to both Ted and each other while they can’t help but mix their personal and professional lives. All of this is going on while we slowly unravel the events that years ago led Ted to leave behind everything and everyone he loved.

The series stars Stephen Amell, Lex Scott Davis, Josh McDermitt and Bryan Greenberg. Aaron Korsh is writer and executive producer. snippet.title: Yuval Raphael - New Day Will Rise | Israel 🇮🇱 | Official Music Video | #Eurovision2025
snippet.description:
Subscribe and 🔔 to Eurovision 👉 https://www.youtube.com/user/eurovision?sub_confirmation=1 ​

Yuval Raphael will represent Israel at the Eurovision Song Contest 2025 with the song New Day Will Rise.

~~~ Lyrics ~~~

New Day Will Rise

And even if you say goodbye 
You’ll never go away 
You are the rainbow of my sky 
My colours in the grey
My only wish upon a star 
Sunshine in the day 
The only song that my piano ever plays 

And even if you say goodbye 
You’ll always be around 
To lift me up and take me high 
Keep my feet close to the ground 
Are you proud of me tonight 
Dreams are coming true 
I choose the light 
Nothing to lose if I lose you 

New day will rise
Life will go on 
Everyone cries 
Don’t cry alone
Darkness will fade  
All the pain will go by 
But we will stay  
Even if you say goodbye 

‏Et même si tu dis adieu
‏Tu ne partiras jamais
‏T’es l’arc-en-ciel de mon ciel bleu
‏Mes couleurs dans le gris
‏Et mon seul souhait sous un ciel d’art
‏Un rayon dans ma journée
‏La seule chanson que mon piano peut  jouer

New day will rise
Life will go on 
Everyone cries 
Don’t cry alone
Darkness will fade  
All the pain will go by 
But we will stay  
Even you say

New day will rise
Life will go on 
Everyone cries 
Don’t cry alone
Darkness will fade  
All the pain will go by 
But you will stay  
The love of my life 

מים רבים 
לא יכבו 
את האהבה 
ונהרות לא ישטפוה 

New day will rise
Everyone cries 
Don’t cry alone
Darkness will fade  
All the pain will go by 
But we will stay  
Even if you say goodbye 

A new day will rise
New day will rise

~~~ Credits ~~~

Lyrics & Music: Keren Peles. Produced & Arranged by Tomer Biran.

French translation: Tamir Hitman 
Acoustic Guitar: Avi Singolda 
Piano, Keyboards, Bass, Drums and Programming: Tomer Biran 
Additional Keyboards: Keren Peles

snippet.title: Overlanding Australia (our new tiny home on wheels)
snippet.description:
A very Aussie 4x4 adventure on Stradbroke "Straddie" Island. Filmed Feb 10-13, 2025. Go to http://DrinkLMNT.com/eamonandbec for a free sample pack with any purchase!

After living in a converted sprinter van for nearly 5 years we thought we'd cracked the code to tiny house on wheels with #vanlife  But, this week we really test ourselves with a brand new setup... a 4X4 truck with a rooftop tent. Not only is it the smallest setup we've ever traveled in but we've also added our 1 year old daughter to the mix. Frankie is such an incredibly adaptable baby but can we really enjoy all that Australia has to offer with a 1 year old child in tow? 

We spot kangaroos, drive a 4X4 rig on some of Australia's most epic beaches and manage to keep up with our mate @MaxandOccy . Make sure you check out his episode for more of our adventures.

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.title: We Lived in the NEW $900,000 Earthroamer LTx
snippet.description:
We got to be the first lucky people to take the brand new, one and only EarthRoamer LTx on a roadtrip through the stunning Utah landscapes of Monument Valley and Valley of the Gods! Use our link https://drinkag1.com/karaandnate to subscribe & save $20 off your first subscription!! 
We hope you enjoy this full tour of the new LTx model, plus an epic adventure with some of the best off grid campsites we've ever seen! Plus Nate casually ran a marathon and has a big announcement ;) 

Episode 955 | Filmed February 2025 | Utah

Here are our past EarthRoamer videos :) We're so happy to be friends with this awesome company who lets us go with them on these awesome adventures!! Thanks Zack for another AMAZING trip!

Who are Kara and Nate?! 

2016-2019: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FuFv4iF8wgg&t=1s 

2020-2024: https://youtu.be/ikAN9e0gBaU?si=G644UGWIqPrOzTYW

Originally from Nashville, Tennessee, we got married 2013 and were super “normal.” I was a teacher and Nate started a small printing business from the spare bedroom of our apartment. 

We discovered the world of “travel hacking” while planning our honeymoon & became addicted ;)

So after 2 years of obsessively saving $35k and over 2 million miles and points, we sold our cars and apartment and left home January 10, 2016 for a “one year” trip around the world.

Our goal was to see as many places as possible before we ran out of money and went back home to “normal life.” We started this channel to share our experiences with friends and family, but quickly fell in love with living on the road and found a new passion for capturing our travels through video. So we did everything we could to keep going.

4 years later, we achieved our new goal of visiting 100 countries and all 7 continents. We had no plans to slow down, until 2020 forced us to ;) Which is when we bought a converted van to start exploring our own country for the first time!

After ~2 years of van life, we are back to full time international traveling! And now we are in our 10TH YEAR of finding the best adventures the world has to offer :) 

We are incredibly grateful to be able to continue doing something we love every day. 😊🎥🌎 Thank you to everyone who has been a part of our journey!

snippet.title: Dolly Parton - If You Hadn’t Been There (Official Audio)
snippet.description:

Lyrics:
(Verse 1)
If you hadn’t been there
Where would I be?
Without your trust
Love and belief
The ups and downs
We’ve always shared
And I wouldn’t be here
If you hadn’t been there

(Verse 2)
If you hadn’t been you
Well who would I be?
You’ve always seen
The best in me
Your loving arms
Have cradled me
You held me close
And I believe

I wouldn’t be here
If you hadn’t been there
Holding my hand
Showing you care
You made me dream
More than I dared
And I wouldn’t be here
If you hadn’t been there

(Bridge)
Oh you are my rock
A soft Place to land
My wings, my confidence
You understand
Your willingness
Beyond compare
No I wouldn’t be here
If you hadn’t been there

I wouldn’t be here
If you hadn’t been there
Pushing me on
When I was scared
I thank God and you
Oh for your loving care
And for giving me love
With more to spare
You made me climb
And top the stairs
I wouldn’t be here
I wouldn’t be here
If you hadn’t been there
Oh I wouldn’t be here
If you hadn’t been there

snippet.title: Squishy Makeovers  Fixing Your Squishies #38
snippet.description:
Welcome to another episode of squishy makeovers, where I transform ugly, used, old, dirty, cheap or unwanted squishies (donated by my subscribers) into my own creations. I repair, paint and cut away for hours on end to complete these. Hopefully you like them. Get used to lots of rainbow and sprinkles, because I am addicted to both!

Don't forget to check out the CHESS SET!
https://moriahelizabethmerch.com/

What I'm Using (contains affiliate links):
Squishy Makeovers Fixing Your Squishies #37
Tulip Matte Fabric Paint: https://amzn.to/49OjdMp
Tulip Slick Fabric Paint: https://amzn.to/3LBW6uO
Posca Pens: https://amzn.to/40TgXPL
Scissors: https://amzn.to/3MjSY6L
Sandpaper: https://amzn.to/3EQOOPY
Fabric Hot Glue: https://amzn.to/3PQ4KZh


_______FAQs________

1. CAN I SEND YOU SQUISHIES?
So many generous people have sent me their unwanted squishies so I actually have a lot to work on already, BUT if you desperately want to, you can request my mailing address in the email ALLLL the way at down in the description (sorry for the traveling), make sure to read the disclaimer down there as well.

2. ARE SQUISHIES RETURNED TO THE SENDERS AFTER THE MAKEOVER?
No. These squishies  are sent as donations to the series because they are damaged and/or no longer wanted. Everyone has been informed in advance that squishies would not be returned. 

3. WHAT PAINT DO YOU USE?
I use fabric paint. Fabric paint is meant to stretch, so it is perfect for squishing! Any brand will work fine, but I mainly use Tulip. You can find it at Michaels, Hobby Lobby, A.C. Moore, Walmart, Joann Fabrics, and Online.

5. WILL FABRIC PAINT CRACK?
The matte fabric paint is more likely to crack after lots of squishing. Slick fabric paints never crack. But there are benefits to both. I usually mix the two paints together to get the best of both worlds.

6. CAN I USE ACRYLIC PAINT ON SQUISHIES?
I would not recommend that. Acrylic paint will either make the squishy hard, or it will crack and flake off very easily.


___UPLOAD SCHEDULE___

Friday at 4:00pm ET

___________WELCOME TO MY CHANNEL__________

Hey! my name is Moriah (pronounced muh-rye-yuh) Elizabeth and this is my channel....obviously. I'm 29 and like doing creative activities (mostly painting on things), or really anything that gives me an excuse to use rainbows, sprinkles and my own cutesy characters in excess. I'm heavy into editing, so my video are chalk full of sound effects, filters and lil....moments, or as we like to call them "MEmes." I paint on squishies, thrift store finds, and various other items I find. I also love to draw, traditionally and digitally. I'm not the most skilled artist out here, but I like to focus on having fun with creativity and being able to laugh at my own mistakes. 

CURRENT SERIES:
Squishy Makeovers: Fixing and decorating used squishies sent from my viewers
Thrift Store Makeovers: Fixing and decorating stuff I find at thrift stores/yard sales
Bake With ME: Recreating squishies I've decorated in real life
Create This Book: Drawing in the prompt book that I wrote (available to purchase and follow along)
Squishy Unboxing: Opening used squishy packages sent from viewers
Drawings to Squishies: turning my flat drawings into squishies
Finishing Art Ideas: Choosing art ideas from my giant list and making them happen
Squishies I've Been Avoiding: Painting on the squishies I DON'T want to paint

https://a.co/4XDtrmV

CREATE THIS BOOK 2:

ME Merchandise:

____CONTACT ME____

FOR BUSINESS INQUIRIES/OPPORTUNITIES ONLY:



_____MAIL ME_____

For sending squishies, Letters, or general fan mail, please contact: FANMAIL@MORIAH.VIDEO to request my P.O. box address

localized.title: Bleaching My Hair At Home *this was a bad idea*
localized.description:
Today we are bleaching my hair at home.. for the first time... 
Hope you enjoyed, Subscribe to be notified when I post! 🍓

OTHER VIDEOS u might like: 🌷✨
Trying Vintage hair tools: https://youtu.be/pN4jSCHuq58

My Socials & fun stuff: 🧸
Instagram https://www.instagram.com/miamaples/
Tiktok https://www.tiktok.com/@realiomiamaples

Thank you so much for being here and watching!
I really hope you enjoyed! 💗

snippet.title: Tropical Cyclone Alfred Timeline: Where and when it will make landfall | 9 News Australia Analysis
snippet.description:
The most populated part of Australia’s east coast is now just hours away from its first cyclone in more than 50 years. Cyclone Alfred continues to approach the Australian coast slowly, spinning up damaging winds and heavy rain. The category 2 storm is expected to cross early on Saturday morning, most likely between Noosa and Coolangatta. It has knocked out power to tens of thousands on the Gold Coast and in northern NSW. | *Subscribe and 🔔: http://9Soci.al/KM6e50GjSK9*

snippet.title: 3-6-2025  Pip 3 Is Here!
snippet.description:
Today at 10:21 we spotted Pip movement in the third egg. You can see the chick's beak moving inside the egg. At 10:53 the Pip site looked a bit larger.

We are under snowy weather today. Jackie and Shadow may hunker down for the whole day and skip the feedings, even though there is plenty of food on the nest. Protecting the chicks from the elements is very important.

They ate very well and had very full crops yesterday, so they should be fine for a few days on the contents of their crops.

Hatching is a long process. It may take a day or more for the chick to fully emerge from the shell. 

We are expecting sunny weather tomorrow. Just in time for the new Chick3!
Meanwhile, we will remain patient and hold the most positive thoughts.
Cali

snippet.title: 2025 Cadillac Escalade V Review // Total Domination
snippet.description:
The 2025 Cadillac Escalade ESV V-Series  ($212,099 starting in Canada, $165,500 starting in the US) has seen several updates for this model year, and is ready to defend its best-selling title. The 6.2 L supercharged V8 engine is unchanged, but it has seen some styling changes inside and out. This includes an absolutely massive 55 inch screen in the dash, carbon fiber trim bits, 24 inch wheels, new light designs and other changes. But does the new Escalade V command its hefty price tag? And are the latest changes in the right direction? Thomas and James can’t wait to find out! We hope you enjoy the episode. Subscribe!

Il motore V8 sovralimentato da 6,2 L è invariato, ma ha visto alcuni cambiamenti di stile dentro e fuori. Ciò include un enorme schermo da 55 pollici nel cruscotto, parti di rifinitura in fibra di carbonio, ruote da 24 pollici, nuovi design delle luci e altre modifiche. Ma la nuova Escalade V comanda il suo pesante cartellino del prezzo? E gli ultimi cambiamenti vanno nella giusta direzione? Thomas e James non vedono l'ora di scoprirlo! Ci auguriamo che ti piaccia l'episodio. Iscriviti!

hi.title: 2025 कैडिलैक एस्केलेड वी समीक्षा // कुल वर्चस्व
hi.description:
2025 कैडिलैक एस्केलेड ESV V-सीरीज (कनाडा में शुरुआती कीमत 212,099 डॉलर, अमेरिका में शुरुआती कीमत 165,500 डॉलर) में इस मॉडल वर्ष के लिए कई अपडेट देखे गए हैं, और यह अपने सबसे ज़्यादा बिकने वाले खिताब को बचाने के लिए तैयार है। 6.2 L सुपरचार्ज्ड V8 इंजन में कोई बदलाव नहीं किया गया है, लेकिन इसके अंदर और बाहर कुछ स्टाइलिंग बदलाव किए गए हैं। इसमें डैश में एक बहुत बड़ी 55 इंच की स्क्रीन, कार्बन फाइबर ट्रिम बिट्स, 24 इंच के पहिए, नई लाइट डिज़ाइन और अन्य बदलाव शामिल हैं। लेकिन क्या नई एस्केलेड V अपनी भारी कीमत के हिसाब से सही है? और क्या नवीनतम बदलाव सही दिशा में हैं? थॉमस और जेम्स यह जानने के लिए बेताब हैं! हमें उम्मीद है कि आपको यह एपिसोड पसंद आएगा। सब्सक्राइब करें! यहाँ देखें हकबेरी के वे कपड़े जो हमने पहने हैं: https://glnk.io/3vzrq/thethrottlehouse652

id.title: Ulasan Cadillac Escalade V 2025 // Dominasi Total
id.description:
Cadillac Escalade ESV V-Series 2025 ($212.099 mulai di Kanada, $165.500 mulai di AS) telah mengalami beberapa pembaruan untuk model tahun ini, dan siap mempertahankan gelarnya sebagai mobil terlaris. Mesin V8 supercharged 6,2 L tidak mengalami perubahan, tetapi telah mengalami beberapa perubahan gaya di dalam dan luar. Ini termasuk layar 55 inci yang sangat besar di dasbor, potongan serat karbon, roda 24 inci, desain lampu baru, dan perubahan lainnya. Namun, apakah Escalade V baru ini pantas dengan banderol harganya yang mahal? Dan apakah perubahan terbaru ini ke arah yang benar? Thomas dan James tidak sabar untuk mengetahuinya! Kami harap Anda menikmati episode ini. Berlanggananlah!

fr-FR.description:
Le Cadillac Escalade ESV Série V 2025 (212 099 $ à partir du Canada, 165 500 $ à partir des États-Unis) a connu plusieurs mises à jour pour cette année modèle et est prêt à défendre son titre de best-seller. Le moteur V8 suralimenté de 6,2 L reste inchangé, mais il a subi quelques changements de style à l'intérieur et à l'extérieur. Cela comprend un écran absolument massif de 55 pouces dans le tableau de bord, des garnitures en fibre de carbone, des roues de 24 pouces, de nouveaux designs d'éclairage et d'autres changements. Mais le nouvel Escalade V justifie-t-il son prix élevé ? Et les derniers changements vont-ils dans la bonne direction ? Thomas et James ont hâte de le découvrir ! snippet.title: CrossFit Open Workout 25.2 Live Announcement, presented by @USBorderPatrol
snippet.description:
Week 2 of the 2025 CrossFit Open takes us to CrossFit Incendia in Peoria, Arizona, with the live announcement of Open Workout #25point2. Watch Games athletes Emily Rolfe and Sydney Wells throw down shortly after the workout is announced.

Week 2 is presented by U.S. Border Patrol → https://cf.games/24_USBP

For full workout details, movement standards, and the official scorecard, visit → https://games.crossfit.com/workouts/open/2025/2

Submit your score via the CrossFit Games app by Monday, March 10, at 5 p.m. PT.  Apple → https://apps.apple.com/us/app/crossfit-games/id825019869

Android → https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.crossfit.games.android&hl=en_US&pli=1

How to watch all live Open announcements → https://games.crossfit.com/article/how-watch-2025-crossfit-open

Learn more about the CrossFit Open here → https://games.crossfit.com/open/overview
—
The CrossFit Games are the ultimate proving grounds for the Fittest Man and Fittest Woman on Earth™ and are world-renowned as the definitive test of fitness. Every year since 2007, fans from around the world have attended the multi-day sporting event, streamed the competition online, or watched on ESPN, CBS, or a wide range of international broadcasts. The international field of play has included athletes from more than 120 countries. The CrossFit Games starts in the qualifying round with 300,000+ athletes competing around the world. Throughout the season the field is whittled down to just 560 athletes.

Learn more about the CrossFit Games → https://cf.games/games-learn-more

Learn more about CrossFit → https://www.crossfit.com/what-is-crossfit/?utm_source=social&utm_medium=youtube&utm_campaign=crossfit

Find a CrossFit gym near you → https://www.crossfit.com/map?utm_source=social&utm_medium=youtube&utm_campaign=crossfit

View CrossFit workouts → https://www.crossfit.com/workout?utm_source=social&utm_medium=youtube&utm_campaign=crossfit

Subscribe to CrossFit email newsletters → https://www.crossfit.com/newsletters/?utm_source=social&utm_medium=youtube&utm_campaign=crossfit

Produit de la génération du millénaire, son appréciation des nouvelles technologies se mêle à son éthique de travail à l'ancienne, et il offre une capacité unique à transmettre son message d'une manière qui résonne auprès des agriculteurs de longue date ainsi que de ceux qui n'ont aucune connaissance de l'agriculture. Avec la sensibilisation croissante des consommateurs à la provenance de leurs aliments, Zach a identifié le besoin d'une voix indépendante en première ligne de l'agriculture. Zach promeut activement l'agriculture en partageant ses expériences quotidiennes dans le monde agricole tout en fournissant une éducation d'agriculteur à agriculteur pour faciliter une conversation collaborative entre les agriculteurs et le public.

Sein Witz und sein trockener Sinn für Humor sprechen Kinder und Erwachsene gleichermaßen an. Als Produkt der Millennial-Generation verbindet sich seine Wertschätzung für neue Technologien mit seiner altmodischen Arbeitsmoral und er verfügt über die einzigartige Fähigkeit, seine Botschaft auf eine Weise zu vermitteln, die sowohl bei langjährigen Landwirten als auch bei jenen Anklang findet, die keine Ahnung von Landwirtschaft haben. Angesichts des wachsenden Bewusstseins der Verbraucher darüber, woher ihre Lebensmittel kommen, hat Zach erkannt, dass eine unabhängige Stimme aus der Landwirtschaftsbranche erforderlich ist. Zach fördert aktiv die Landwirtschaft, indem er seine täglichen Erfahrungen in der Landwirtschaftswelt teilt und gleichzeitig Landwirt für Landwirt Bildung vermittelt, um einen gemeinsamen Dialog zwischen Landwirten und der Öffentlichkeit zu ermöglichen.

snippet.title: Primitive Technology: Water powered forge blower
snippet.description:
Primitive Technology: Water powered forge blower
Subscribe: http://bit.ly/subPT | Never miss a video! Enable ‘ALL’ Notifications!

Weapons: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLGnWLXjIDnpA-XGDrrmVgBnSXx15i2Awp&playnext=1&index=2
Popular Videos: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLGnWLXjIDnpAb29Lrdki5BPjTpMon8zla&playnext=1&index=2

About This Video:
I made a water powered forge blower to blow air into a furnace. Getting running water to power a blower had been on my list for a while now and the weather had been wet enough to cause enough flow in the creek to try one. A significant part of the labour in doing an iron smelt comes from the operation of the air supply (unless natural draft is used). The current air supply method I use was a hand powered, centrifugal fan encased in a housing as seen in previous videos.

 I had a 2 ideas as to how to automate this with water power. The first method was to build a large, slow water wheel and run a rope belt around it linking it to the smaller, faster fan rotor to spin it. I tried this and it kept having issues due to the rope not spinning the blower effectively and also the fact that the water level changed and the wheel stopped moving. 

The second idea was to use a small diameter water wheel directly connected to the fan rotor with a water spout dropping the flow onto the wheel at a height. This turned out to be the simplest and most effective of the methods with rotor speeds between 6 and 8 revolutions a second being attained. The then encased the fan inside the existing blower housing and tested the blower on a furnace build in front of it. The blower did indeed work though not as powerfully as a hand powered one.

With some adjustments, the blower may be improved so it becomes competitive with the hand powered method. The water powered method will go endlessly without human effort and does not wear out any rope as does the hand powered method. It's simple and reliable and I'll be doing more experiments with it in future. 

00:00-00:23 Wet season and Furnace
00:23-01:26 Toy water wheel
1:26-08:59 Design 1, Large wheel, belt drive and fan 
08:59-16:14 Design 2, Small wheel, direct drive fan
16:14-18:44 Fire by friction
18:44-19:48 Igniting furnace, last minute adjustments
19:48-22:33 Testing water powered forge blower

About Primitive Technology:
Primitive technology is a hobby where you build things in the wild completely from scratch using no modern tools or materials. These are the strict rules: If you want a fire, use a fire stick - An axe, pick up a stone and shape it - A hut, build one from trees, mud, rocks etc. The challenge is seeing how far you can go without utilizing modern technology. I do not live in the wild, but enjoy building shelter, tools, and more, only utilizing natural materials. To find specific videos, visit my playlist tab for building videos focused on pyrotechnology, shelter, weapons, food & agriculture, tools & machines, and weaving & fiber.

#PrimitiveTechnology #water  #forge #fire

snippet.title: Something Strange Happens When You Trust Quantum Mechanics
snippet.description:
Does light take all possible paths at the same time? 🌏 Get exclusive NordVPN deal here ➵  https://NordVPN.com/veritasium It’s risk free with Nord’s 30 day money-back guarantee!✌

A massive thank you to Dr. Andrew Mitchell for all his help and expertise. If you want to delve further into this topic then we highly recommend his lecture on Classical physics derived from quantum mechanics: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2iuLwWDYC4U&t=1s

We’re incredibly grateful to Prof. David Kaiser, Prof. Steven Strogatz, Prof. Geraint F. Lewis, Elba Alonso-Monsalve, Prof. Christopher S. Baird, Prof. Anthony Bloch, and Prof. Stephen Bartlett for their invaluable contributions to this video.

A special thanks to Mahesh Shenoy from FloatHeadPhysics for his help with this video. Check out his excellent intuitive video on the UV Catastrophe here (Sep 2024): https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ALEDjjAVZSY 

▀▀▀
0:00 What path does light travel?
2:40 Black Body Radiation
6:47 How did Planck solve the ultraviolet catastrophe?
9:42 The Quantum of Action
13:25 De Broglie’s Hypothesis 
15:16 The Double Slit Experiment
20:00 How Feynman Did Quantum Mechanics
25:01 Proof That Light Takes Every Path
31:16 The Theory of Everything

▀▀▀
Sign up to our Patreon to submit your Q&A questions: https://ve42.co/PatreonLA2  

Try Snatoms! A molecular modelling kit I invented where the atoms snap together.

▀▀▀

Planck's law. In Wikipedia - https://ve42.co/planckslaw

Einstein and The Photoelectric Effect. (Jan 2005) via APS News - https://ve42.co/einsteinphotoelec 
Louis de Broglie (1924). On the Theory of Quanta.  - https://ve42.co/theoryquanta 
Larry Sorensen (2012). Path Integrals 1. University of Washington - https://ve42.co/pathintegrals 
Feynman’s Method of “A Particle Exploring All Possible Paths”. (Mar 2018) via Pure Dhamma - https://ve42.co/allposspaths 
A great intuitive video on the Feynman path integral approach - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Sp5SvdDh2u8&t=1253s 
Origins of Quantum Theory. via University of Pittsburgh - https://ve42.co/origquanttheor

Edison incandescent lights by William J. Hammer via Wikimedia Commons - https://ve42.co/edinclights

Muon Ray. (2011). https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-QUj2ZRUa7c
Muon Ray. (2011). https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1C7abO7LtV0
Bohrs Atomic Model via EEEGUIDE.COM - https://ve42.co/bohrmodel

snippet.title: Kevin Hart shocks Regina Hall with surprise TODAY appearance
snippet.description:
TODAY’s Jenna Bush Hager stunned her guest co-host Regina Hall with a very special surprise appearance from comedian and entrepreneur Kevin Hart! Hart opens up about his friendship with Hall, sharing a variety of funny stories – including the time he invited her over but didn’t let her through his house’s gate! Then, he discusses his upcoming animated series, “Lil Kev,” and presents the co-hosts with their own “lil” versions.

snippet.title: TC Alfred Perfection at Kirra! Biggest Swell in Years Slams Gold Coast
snippet.description:
We first began tracking Tropical Cyclone Alfred in late February. It wasn’t clear how surfable the swell would be, but as it turns out, Alfred was very, very surfable —especially at Kirra—and will be talked about for years to come.

Notably, Alfred is also the first cyclone to make landfall in Southern Queensland in 51 years, with its landfall occurring just as we go to press. The full impact of this storm will continue to unfold in the coming days. 

As for the surf? “People are charging,” said Queensland surfer Korbin Hutchings. “It’s gnarly out at Kirra—wide, thick, heavy, and shallow. You’re getting lit up out there. The swell is relentless.”

Residents of Queensland are advised to stay informed through local resources for the latest updates.

Filmed by: Jesse Little, Dan Scott, Huw Williams, Charlie Cullen and Andy Potts
Edited by: Michael Weybret

Thumbnail photo: Simon "Swilly" Williams

En este explosivo video musical, Yailin La Más Viral y DJ Adonis nos sumergen en una historia de pasión, rencor y recuerdos que nunca se borran. Con una mezcla de ritmos contagiosos y letras cargadas de sentimiento, ambos artistas relatan un amor de amenazas y huellas imborrables. Aunque intentan seguir adelante, hay cosas que simplemente no se pueden OLVIDAR. Entre escenas intensas y un beat envolvente, este video promete convertirse en un himno para todos los que han sentido que el pasado aún los persigue.  
Director: Starlyn Javier

¿Será una historia de revancha, nostalgia o un amor que se niega a morir? Descúbrelo en este impactante estreno.

snippet.title: 3-3-2025  A pip!...And Another!...And…! 🐥
snippet.description:
Sunday afternoon, as Jackie and Shadow shouted away an unseen intruder, the first ‘pip’ was confirmed on one of the eggs! (egg on the right)– A pip, or slight crack in the egg shell, is the first sign that the chick is working to hatch out.

By Monday morning, a pip was visible on the 2nd egg! –
Jackie and Shadow’s delayed incubation worked to make the chicks hatch closer together and be close to the same size.

Jackie was obviously feeling the movement underneath her as she kept looking down and standing up to roll the eggs much more than usual. Shadow happily got a turn on the eggs to give Jackie a morning break.

By mid-morning, the chick’s beak was visible and tiny chirps could be heard…

When Shadow came to check in, Jackie stood and seemed to be telling him about the development…one chick could be seen moving inside. Jackie wouldn’t let Shadow have his turn. She was too invested to leave.

It took Shadow 4 more visits—2 sticks and 1 fluff—before Jackie let him take over for a short time. Now, both holes were bigger…and his turn came with lots of the soft talking instructions from Mama Jackie before she left.

Jackie soon returned with a fish that got left on the side of the nest, ready for feeding.

By afternoon, Jackie increased her soft talking to almost continuous, seeming to be encouraging her chicks to keep up the great progress. Both holes were growing and now big enough to easily see a moving beak inside each one.

As evening came, the holes grew more, tiny cheeps could be heard, and Shadow figured out he was unlikely to get another turn. He flew off to roost nearby.

…but boy will he be surprised in the morning!…before midnight, the first chick had its wing and head visible and a short time later, it was out! Jackie pushed it back in a bit as she rolled the eggs, but it’s first touch down will be the official hatch time: 23:26, cam time.

The 2nd egg is moving forward quickly on its hatching process.

And the 3rd egg is still only on Day 34. Normal hatchings are 35-42 days, so still plenty of time to wait and watch what happens with it.
Welcome to the world, Chick#1!
Sandy


Friends of Big Bear Valley (FOBBV) https://friendsofbigbearvalley.org/
Public Facebook Page (no account needed): https://www.facebook.com/FOBBV/
Private Facebook Group (more content): https://www.facebook.com/groups/fobbv
